s roles ‚Üí 200 with JSON array\n  - `POST /authz/check`       ‚Äî check permission; body: `{\"userId\": \"<string>\", \"permission\": \"<string>\"}` ‚Üí 200 with `{\"allowed\": <bool>}`\n","numLines":31,"startLine":1,"totalLines":31}}}
